         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">24/1/85 ¶  ¶ Today, dear Mr Holtze, I tried to describe your  ¶ Trichosanthus ¶  No. 432 ¶  (the Cucurbitacea with white fringed flowers). However, as the fruits are lacking, I cannot complete the des...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">85.01.24</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Maurice Holtze</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">GRG 19/391, State Records of South Australia, Adelaide.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">24/1/85</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Heute, lieber Herr Holtze, versuchte ich Ihren </seg>
               <seg style="color: #000000; ">
                  <name key="Trichosanthus">Trichosanthus</name>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> zu beschreiben, N. 432 (die Cucurbitacee mit weissen gefranzten Blumen; da aber die Früchte fehlen, kann ich die Beschreibung nicht vollenden. Würden Sie mir einige Früchte u noch mehr Blumen u Blätter mit </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Post</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> senden?</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Freundlichst grüssend</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">24/1/85</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>Today, dear Mr Holtze, I tried to describe your <seg style="color: #000000; font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Trichosanthus">Trichosanthus</name>
               </seg> No. 432<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Trichosanthes</seg>? See M to M. Holtze, December 1886 (in this edition as 86-12-00); M to M. Holtze, 3 December 1886 (in this edition as 86-12-03b); and M to M. Holtze, 12 December 1886.</p>
               </note> (the Cucurbitacea with white fringed flowers). However, as the fruits are lacking, I cannot complete the description. Would you send me a few fruits and also more flowers and leaves by <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">mail</hi>
               </seg>?<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M described the species, without seeing the fruit, as <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Trichosanthes holtzei</seg> in B86.12.01, p. 447, from the specimen MEL 100084.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Most friendly greetings</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Trichosanthus">Trichosanthus</name>
            </p>
         </div>
